source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_00<tab>Bhirdraeg seeks to restore equilibrium by having the local fauna culled.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_00<tab>サマーフォード庄のビルドレーグは、ラノシアオレンジの育成を妨げる魔物退治を依頼したいようだ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_01<tab>Puks prey on the insects that pollinate La Noscean oranges, upsetting the balance of nature on Summerford Farms. Assist Bhirdraeg by culling five puk hatchlings.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_01<tab>ラノシアオレンジの受粉を助ける益虫を食ってしまう「プーク・ハッチリング」を5体駆除しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_02<tab>You have carried out the culling as bade. Return to Bhirdraeg and inform him that the puks stop here.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_02<tab>プーク・ハッチリングを討伐することができた。「サマーフォード庄」の「ビルドレーグ」に報告しよう。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_03<tab>With the bees back about their business, the La Noscean oranges will grow. Nevertheless, all will be for naught if the lazing pirates let the fruit rot on the boughs.
target: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_SEQ_03<tab>害獣を間引くことができたものの、ラノシアオレンジの収穫量を増やすには、海賊上がりの農夫たちの手伝いが不可欠だろう。彼らが、農業にまじめに取り組む日が来るのだろうか。
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_TODO_00<tab>プーク・ハッチリングを駆除

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_1<tab>La Noscean orange nectar is sweet, but rest assured it's paid for in sweat.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_1果樹園のラノシアオレンジは、見事だったろ？
だがなぁ、こいつを実らせるのは大変なんだ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_2<tab>We have to pollinate each orange by hand because of the blasted puks that prey on the nearby bees.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_2花粉を運ぶ小さな蜜蜂を
プークどもが根こそぎ食っちまうもんで、
俺たちがひとつ、ひとつ手で受粉させてんのさ。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_3<tab>If we could only eradicate some five puk hatchlings, it would save us from having to do nature's work.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_3そうだ、君は冒険者なんだろ？
プークの幼生体……プーク・ハッチリングを
5体ほど、狩ってきてくれんか？

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_11<tab>The buzz on the wind tells me you've done the deed.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_11首尾は上々のようだな。これで、花咲く季節の重労働が、
少しは楽になるといいんだが……。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_12<tab>The only pests plaguin' my orchard are those woeful whelps-out-of-water.
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_12まぁ、それもこれも海賊上がりの連中が、
素直にシャキシャキ働いてくれりゃ、いいって話なんだがね。

source: TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_13<tab>If only you could rid me of the parasitic pirates as you did the pesky puks!
target:
TEXT_SUBSEA061_00473_BHIRDRAEG_000_13やれやれ……君に駆除を頼むべきは、プークじゃなくて
海賊上がりの連中だったかもな、ハッハッハ。
